{
  "stem": "11882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I had no money when I left Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'll tell you something that may shock you, but it's really funny from my point of view, but it may not be funny to anyone else after all we've gone through.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had a terrible train ride.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was the last train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The reason I got on the train that Saturday afternoon, evening, was because the radio said, Holland will close the border at midnight tonight from people coming out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I thought, well, it's time for me to get over there then.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] helped me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I packed a few little things together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I left everything else; my little room and all my little bit of possessions which I had there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] came to the train with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she said, I have a feeling we won't see each other for a long time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she waved goodbye to me at the railway station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I thought, oh, I'm coming back next week, I hope.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But anyway, I went to Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But as I crossed the border, I wonder if I should tell you what happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was really, to me, funny, and I survived it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But it's not very-- maybe many people may pick it up in a very-- after all we've been through, in a way, that it really wasn't-- sincerely, it really wasn't.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had a hell of a ride on the train out from them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Stopping.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was full of people who had come probably, I don't know where, from Czechoslovakia, whose little possessions seemed to be-- I don't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was only standing room on this train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We stood so tight in that train, you couldn't fall over in any direction.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
